vie  sesame street aladdin episode   boston public laurence williams episode chapter fortytwo  the proud family reuben voice episode behind family lines – life with bonnie david bellows  episodes nominated – image award for best supporting actor in a comedy series satellite award for best supporting actor – television series – crank yankers various voices  episodes  samurai jack da samuraijunk monster voice episode samurai versus samurai – my wife and kids jimmy  episodes  thank god youre here host  episodes  bones professor bunsen jude episode the body and the bounty  law  order special victims unit jeremy swift episode branded  happy endings terry chuckles episode in the heat of the noche  randy cunningham th grade ninja rudd rhymez voice episode hip hopocalypse now  the soul man jesse episode obama drama  bad teacher carl gaines  episodes  black dynamite doctor voice episode how honeybee got her groove back or night of the living dickheads – comedy bang bang network president recurring role  episodes –present the carmichael show joe carmichael main cast  episodes  the mccarthys dr hugh morris episode family therapy  cutthroat kitchen himselfjudge episode taco dirty to me  the wiz live the cowardly lion  robert the farmhand man  live performance  the eric andre show himselfdavid alan thicke episode dennis rodman haley joel osment  snap decision host referencesedit  katsilometes john july   albino gorillas farrakhan the musical with grier anything is possible las vegas sun retrieved july     david alan grier biography retrieved    david alan grier biography  wwwfilmreferencecom in eng retrieved  cs maint unrecognized language link  a b king larry  may  david alan grier video interview larry king now retrieved  august    aww here it goes to hollywood part  on imdb   tony nominations announced fela and la cage top list archived from the original on  retrieved    david alan grier broadwaycom retrieved    th annual grammy awards winners  nominees grammycom retrieved   