torney information with the supreme court of ohio  find more information about david alan young on the supreme court of ohio and the ohio judiciary website including registration status and disciplinary history david allan young  wikipedia david allan young from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search this article has an unclear citation style the references used may be made clearer with a different or consistent style of citation footnoting or external linking september  learn how and when to remove this template message david allan young jr may   wilkinsburg pennsylvania  june   louisville kentucky was an american entomologist who specialized in the taxonomy of the cicadellidae and authored a comprehensive treatment of the family with numerous genera and species described and named by him life and workedit david youngs father was a traveling salesman and he attended school in western pennsylvania and high school in louisville he studied at the university of louisville and graduated with a bachelor of arts in  he then taught science at the louisville public school system and later studied entomology at the cornell university and obtained a master of science in  he then joined the us army as a private and was honorably discharged as a first lieutenant in  he then became an instructor in the biology department at the university of louisville he worked under dr r h beamer and obtained a doctorate in entomology in  he then worked as a taxonomist in the united states national museum washington dc working on the identification of insects in the quarantine procedures of the united states department of agriculture he took up a position of an associate professor at the north carolina state university in  and continued his systematic work on leafhoppers his work on the world fauna of leafhoppers included descriptions of  new species new genera and a new tribe his taxonomic study of the cicadellinae homopteracicadellidae with  pages covered  genera around the world and was published in three parts between  and  jp kramer  proceedings of the entomological society of washington  declared part  of it as the most outstanding and most comprehensive single volume ever produced on a large segment of the cicadellidae his work was honored by the north carolina entomological society with an award for outstanding contribution to entomology in  he was a fellow of the washington academy of science he died of an aneurysm on  june  the da young memorial symposium characters for the higher classification of cicadellidae was held in his honor at the th international auchenorrhyncha congress in delphi greece august  a leafhopper species neolaccogrypota youngi from peru has been named after him selected publicationsedit young d a  taxonomic study of the cicadellinae homoptera cicadellidae part  proconiini bull us nat mus – young d a  taxonomic study of the cicadellinae homoptera cicadellidae part  new world cicadellini and the genus cicadella north carolina agric exp sta tech bull – young d a  taxonomic study of the cicadellinae homoptera cicadellidae part  old world cicadellini north carolina agric res ser tech bull – young d a jr  the leafhopper tribe alebrini homoptera cicadellidae proceedings of the united states national museum   referencesedit  costes danice h  michael d webb  four new species of neotropical spittlebugs hemiptera cercopidae tomaspidinae revista brasileira de entomologia    ncsu biography biography authority control worldcat identities viaf  isni     bnf cbp data retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitledavidallanyoungoldid categories american entomologistspeople from louisville kentucky births deathsthcentury zoologiststhcentury american scientistshidden categories wikipedia references cleanup from september all articles needing references cleanuparticles covered by wikiproject wikify from september all articles covered by wikiproject wikifywikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with isni